ic compositions of forming planets, as well as to relate observed\natmospheric C/O ratios of exoplanets to where and how the atmospheres have\nformed in a disk midplane, chemical evolution needs to be considered and\nimplemented into planet formation models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Sep 2017 17:38:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
