t thermal pulse that\nturns O-rich PNe into C-rich PNe is discarded, except in three objects, that\nshow C/O > 1. We also discuss the possibility of a He pre-enrichment to explain\nthe most He-enriched objects. We cannot discard other scenarios like extra\nmixing, stellar rotation or binary interactions to explain the chemical\nabundances behaviour observed in our sample.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Sep 2017 21:32:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
