at the principles can\ncertainly be extended to particles of other shapes (such as nanospheres,\nnanodisks, and many other experimentally feasible geometries).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Sep 2017 04:59:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-26"}
